##########################
# Ubuntu
##########################

STEP 1
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Install MySQL and create the forum data base.

STEP 2
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Download phpBB-3.X.zip

$ unzip phpBB-3.X.zip /var/www

$ mv phpBB-3.X.zip forum

STEP 3
---------------------------------------------------------------------

$ cd forum

$ sudo chmod 666 config.php
$ sudo chmod 777 store
$ sudo chmod 777 cache
$ sudo chmod 777 files
$ sudo chmod 777 images/avatars/upload

STEP 4
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Configure apache2/sites-available/default forum.reset.etsii.upm.es virtualhost.

STEP 5
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Access forum.reset.etsii.upm.es/install/install.php and follow the steps.

STEP 6
---------------------------------------------------------------------

$ sudo chmod 644 config.php

$ sudo rm -rf install
$ sudo rm -rf docs
$ sudo rm ../phpBB-3.X.zip





